---

import Rmc from '../../assets/icons/rmc.webp';
import Netflix from '../../assets/icons/netflix.webp';
import Amazon from '../../assets/icons/amazon.webp';
import Sponsors from './Sponsors.astro';
---

<section class="bg-secondary py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Partners / Sponsors -->
  <Sponsors />

  <!-- Problem Statement -->
  <div class="animate-on-scroll container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center mt-16 sm:mt-20 md:mt-24 gap-12 sm:gap-14 lg:gap-16">
    <!-- Visual composition with subscription logos -->
    <aside class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative h-[350px] sm:h-[400px] md:h-[450px] lg:h-[500px] flex items-center justify-center lg:block" aria-label="Exemples d'abonnements populaires">
      <figure class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 lg:left-10 lg:translate-x-0 w-32 h-32 sm:w-40 sm:h-40 md:w-52 md:h-52 bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center p-6 sm:p-8 transform -rotate-6 z-10">
        <img src={Netflix.src} alt="Logo Netflix" class="w-full h-full object-contain" width="208" height="208" loading="lazy" />
      </figure>
      <figure class="absolute top-24 sm:top-28 md:top-32 left-1/2 translate-x-16 lg:left-60 lg:translate-x-0 w-32 h-32 sm:w-40 sm:h-40 md:w-52 md:h-52 bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center p-6 sm:p-8 transform rotate-12 z-20">
        <img src={Amazon.src} alt="Logo Amazon Prime" class="w-full h-full object-contain" width="208" height="208" loading="lazy" />
      </figure>
       <figure class="absolute top-48 sm:top-52 md:top-60 left-1/2 -translate-x-16 lg:left-20 lg:translate-x-0 w-32 h-32 sm:w-40 sm:h-40 md:w-52 md:h-52 bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center p-6 sm:p-8 transform -rotate-3 z-30">
        <img src={Rmc.src} alt="Logo RMC Sport" class="w-full h-full object-contain" width="208" height="208" loading="lazy" />
      </figure>
    </aside>

    <!-- Problem description -->
    <article class="animate-on-scroll w-full lg:w-1/2">
      <h2 class="font-sans font-semibold text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-black mb-6 sm:mb-8 md:mb-12 leading-tight">
        Tu ne sais plus vraiment combien te coûtent tes abonnements chaque mois ?
      </h2>
      <p class="font-sans text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-[#3d3d3d] mb-3 sm:mb-4">
        Tu n’es clairement pas seul : entre Netflix, Spotify, ton forfait mobile, les applis du quotidien et les services en ligne, il devient très facile de perdre le contrôle.
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg text-black leading-relaxed">
        Chaque mois, des millions d’étudiants et de jeunes actifs paient pour des abonnements qu’ils ont oubliés, qu’ils n’utilisent plus… ou dont ils ne voient même plus passer les prélèvements.
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg text-black leading-relaxed">
        Streaming, Internet, stockage, logiciels, services… les paiements s’accumulent discrètement et finissent par plomber ton budget sans prévenir.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
